            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>雪佛龍(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVX-US</a>)截至台北時間09日02:10股價下跌11.29美元，報190.25美元，跌幅5.6%，成交量11,002,261（股），盤中最高價192.30美元、最低價188.60美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+2.51%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+2.22%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+2.69%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+6.09%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>雪佛龍(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CVX:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CVX\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CVX-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-2.59%</li> <li>近 1 月：+6.11%</li> <li>近 3 月：+29.86%</li> <li>近 6 月：+30.1%</li> <li>今年以來：+32.24%</li></ul></section></main>",
